sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant UI as Paywall / Upgrade CTA
    participant Web as create-checkout (edge)
    participant Stripe as Stripe Checkout
    participant Hook as stripe-webhook (edge, verify_jwt=false)
    participant DB as user_entitlements + payment_audit_log
    participant Store as entitlementsStore
    participant Check as check-subscription (edge)

    U->>UI: Click "Upgrade to Explorer"
    UI->>Web: POST /create-checkout (JWT)
    Web->>Stripe: stripe.checkout.sessions.create(...)
    Stripe-->>Web: { url }
    Web-->>UI: redirect URL
    UI->>U: window.location = stripe url
    U->>Stripe: complete payment
    Stripe-->>Hook: webhook checkout.session.completed (signed)
    Hook->>Hook: verify STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET signature
    Hook->>DB: UPSERT user_entitlements; APPEND payment_audit_log
    Hook-->>Stripe: 200 OK
    UI->>Check: POST /check-subscription on return
    Check->>DB: SELECT user_entitlements
    Check-->>UI: { plan, status, entitlements }
    UI->>Store: setFromStripe(...)
